{"tid":2383626,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生被控管有金屬棍 律政司覆核得直 改判監3個月 原審官曾以中大生獲守行為指判監非常遺憾","createTime":"2021-01-28T04:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T09:31:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ef0bca654270afc4b1dd1a4ade9281e820b012","tid":2383626,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:35:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13281&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=8c33c39d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13281</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第一庭 #刑期覆核<br />\n#潘兆初高等法院首席法官<br />\n#彭偉昌上訴庭法官<br />\n#潘敏琦法官<br />\n👤司徒 #1105沙田 #攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n控罪：在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n被指於2019年11月5日於沙田大會堂外管有兩支金屬棍。<br />\n<br />\n背景：被告在2020年8月31日在 #溫紹明署理主任裁判官 席前認罪後，溫官即日判處被告監禁10天。律政司長不滿刑期過輕，向上訴庭提出刑期覆核，並在2021年1月28日處理。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n結果：<br />\n上訴庭批准律政司的覆核申請，並以8個月作量刑起點，考慮各因素改判答辯人監禁3個月。"},{"pid":"cc5b79f29d4ce3c55b29ab5c79d50379ecc06d71","tid":2383626,"uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"原審:<br />\n在專上學院修讀日語及文化研究的男學生去年在街上被警截查，搜出兩支改裝金屬棍，因而被控《公安條例》下在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪。辯方兩度去信律政司，望以簽保守行為方式結案，或以刑罰較輕的《簡易程序治罪條例》起訴，均被拒絕。男生昨在21歲生辰認罪，署理主任裁判官溫紹明認為律政司「苛刻」，拒給年輕人機會，並重提中大內地生揮刀卻准守行為，指律政司對兩案的處理手法「落差太大」，只能惋惜地判男入獄10天，坦言「非常遺憾」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/5UP4TDFHOJA7DGLM7BLRY5HJDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2F5UP4TDFHOJA7DGLM7BLRY5HJDM%2F&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=115188e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2F5UP4TDFHOJA7DGLM7BLRY5HJDM%2F&h=5d6bcfcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/5UP4TDFHOJA7DGLM7BLRY5HJDM/</a>"},{"pid":"7ed07fca01adc32d71e547f53e40a1123c059a6e","tid":2383626,"uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"10日變8個月，上次揮刀點解Dept of Joke唔告"},{"pid":"f63e1a71c71ec700876e49ec78c8bfac605cf363","tid":2383626,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ed07fca01adc32d71e547f53e40a1123c059a6e","tid":2383626,"uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"10日變8個月，上次揮刀點解Dept of Joke唔告"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a7947642a6f9b43fd59a7608f3862da8e992fc","tid":2383626,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92d259b7acf4394755722172574917aee1419ab","tid":2383626,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:39:10.000Z","msg":"多個零月姐  潘書記話輕手左架啦！"},{"pid":"4cf881afdbe7718b41389af8c6b80feb66b64351","tid":2383626,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ed07fca01adc32d71e547f53e40a1123c059a6e","tid":2383626,"uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"10日變8個月，上次揮刀點解Dept of Joke唔告"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"三個月"},{"pid":"1b096af548b5bcbc574d4c59a70547a447f9b928","tid":2383626,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fff495c58418545275df75ff0c7abb35bc68cd0","tid":2383626,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"覆核狗"},{"pid":"1e31116a0004c01b3f19cc0d2d08f42e256262b4","tid":2383626,"uid":287670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8ef0bca654270afc4b1dd1a4ade9281e820b012","tid":2383626,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:35:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13281&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=8c33c39d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13281</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第一庭 #刑期覆核<br />\n#潘兆初高等法院首席法官<br />\n#彭偉昌上訴庭法官<br />\n#潘敏琦法官<br />\n👤司徒 #1105沙田 #攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n控罪：在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n被指於2019年11月5日於沙田大會堂外管有兩支金屬棍。<br />\n<br />\n背景：被告在2020年8月31日在 #溫紹明署理主任裁判官 席前認罪後，溫官即日判處被告監禁10天。律政司長不滿刑期過輕，向上訴庭提出刑期覆核，並在2021年1月28日處理。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n結果：<br />\n上訴庭批准律政司的覆核申請，並以8個月作量刑起點，考慮各因素改判答辯人監禁3個月。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"859ea091a090201f9bf8d0cd5ab982e279c273d8","tid":2383626,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"上訴庭裁定10天刑期過輕，而且原則上出錯，改為以8個月為量刑起點。法庭考慮到被告接受第二次監禁可能會引起焦慮不安，以及覆核時間離案發甚遠，再予以酌情扣減至判囚3個月。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">律政司高級助理刑事檢控專員余國慧</span></strong>質疑，原審裁判官判刑時，過分強調男生沒有使用鐵通，以及他並非現場被捕兩點，而過於輕判採納15天為量刑起點。被告所承認的在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，成立要旨是為預防用途，故裁判官不應視被告沒有使用武器傷人為輕判理由，反而應接納社會氛圍為考慮因素。而且<strong><span class=\"red\">原審裁判官在判辭中解釋為何採納15天為起點時，著墨不足，反而在字裏行間中過分表現對被告人的惋惜和同情，律政司認為做法並不公道。</span></strong>另外，涉案武器屬改裝武器，縱使被告承認是為自衞用途，但刑期似乎與阻嚇性原則相違背。<br />\n<br />\n辯方大律師黎家傑陳詞指，判辭已反映原審裁判官已考慮到控罪的預防性成立要旨，裁判官的決定是基於男生的年紀，其被捕地點並非衝突現場，而且沒有證據反映他曾使用武器。即使鐵通是遭改裝，但攻擊力也不屬於高，因為每支僅重逾一百克。雖然裁判官在判辭中表達同情甚至歉意，但法庭在判刑時是可以有個別意見，內容亦不見得裁判官有因此而減刑。"},{"pid":"26dcc6e423eb37739540cce047f01ac4ed5af1b9","tid":2383626,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:42:52.000Z","msg":"8個月量刑<br />\n咁香淑嫻果單藍屍揸刀3個月量刑幾時覆核？"},{"pid":"dc3f66584d7ffeacafd35f89f03a14eff3ac0ba3","tid":2383626,"uid":95577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"八個月量刑起點真係痴線"},{"pid":"4976370b74eab538f1bd6294d65894f54d31abfe","tid":2383626,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:44:04.000Z","msg":"中大支那狗就撤控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb97ba141ec0c7853338fdc30072338fe498c76","tid":2383626,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"點解扣到三個月 扣咁多？"},{"pid":"4acaa1f9707f97e1af7e2fe67b48d09f898b7260","tid":2383626,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"中国豬揸刀就撤控"},{"pid":"9fc005bca1915af280ed7c17b131ed14478c7a49","tid":2383626,"uid":238828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"45bf4fbe7e763be72397e3d7493e6641b61a99dc","tid":2383626,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eb97ba141ec0c7853338fdc30072338fe498c76","tid":2383626,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"點解扣到三個月 扣咁多？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:48:28.000